Adventuring is a hard life. With a cook along on the journey, your meals will be much better than the typical mix
of hardtack and dried fruit. A satchel of cook's utensils includes a metal pot,
knives, forks, a stirring spoon, and a ladle.

!! Uses for {{!!title}}

You might use {{!!title}} in order to:

* Create a filling meal, or duplicate a meal.
* Spot poison or impurities in food.
* When foraging for food, make do with scavenged ingredients.
* Transform medicine that is bitter or sour into a pleasing concoction.